m65 x20 h13 y60 ff5 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Christ in Collision </div><div class="t m66 x21 h13 y60 ff2 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and </div><div class="t m67 x1f h13 y61 ff5 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Luke a Plagiarist? </div><div class="t m68 xe h13 y62 ff2 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">as well as numerous journal articles. </div><div class="t m69 x1f h13 y63 ff2 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">He and his wife, Janet, a psychologist, have a married </div><div class="t m6a x1f h13 y64 ff2 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">daughter and two grandsons. </div><div class="t m6b x22 h14 y65 ff2 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Check with your local Adventist Book Center </div><div class="t m6c x22 h14 y66 ff2 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for the companion book to the Sabbath School </div><div class="t m6d x22 h14 y67 ff2 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">lessons. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
